description: Generous floor-through condominiums, located in the highly sought-after City Point neighborhood of South Boston. 832 E Third St is an exclusive offering, comprising of a lavish, floor-through condominium. Ideally situated moments from Farragut Road, Pleasant Bay and Castle Island. This wonderfully crafted residence is flooded with light, and flaunts high-end finishes, including: Thermador appliances, quartz countertops, two-tone cabinets, oak hardwood floors, gas fireplace, wine fridge, brilliant outdoor spaces, custom millwork, cabinetry & built-ins, among many more extravagant features. Offering a spacious floor plan totaling 2,359 sf, with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, laundry room, office, dry-bar, deeded parking, on-site storage, and roof rights. The Developer is a master finish carpenter by trade, and you'll notice the quality touches throughout these homes. This is a must see.
